{"text_id":224451,"tokens":["How"," to"," Run"," Longer"," and"," Faster","\n\n","Running"," is"," a"," fantastic"," way"," to"," get"," in"," shape"," and"," improve"," your"," overall"," health",","," but"," it"," can"," be"," tough"," to"," get"," started","."," Whether"," you","'","re"," a"," beginner"," or"," an"," experienced"," runner",","," there"," are"," ways"," to"," improve"," your"," endurance"," and"," speed","."," With"," a"," little"," patience"," and"," practice",","," you"," can"," learn"," how"," to"," run"," longer"," and"," faster",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1",":"," Prepare"," for"," Your"," Run","**","\n\n","\"","Choose"," a"," time"," of"," day"," that"," you"," like"," to"," run",".\""," Running"," at"," the"," same"," time"," every"," day"," can"," help"," make"," it"," a"," habit","."," Some"," people"," prefer"," running"," in"," the"," morning",","," while"," others"," prefer"," the"," evening","."," Experiment"," to"," find"," what"," works"," best"," for"," you",".","\n\n","\"","Create"," a"," music"," playlist",".\""," Listening"," to"," music"," can"," help"," distract"," you"," from"," fatigue"," and"," make"," your"," run"," more"," enjoyable","."," Choose"," upbeat"," songs"," that"," motivate"," you"," to"," keep"," moving",".","\n\n","\"","Altern","ately",","," try"," running"," without"," music",".\""," Some"," runners"," prefer"," not"," to"," listen"," to"," music",","," as"," it"," can"," be"," a"," distraction"," and"," make"," it"," harder"," to"," focus"," on"," their"," breathing"," and"," pace",".","\n\n","\"","Wear"," comfortable"," clothing"," in"," layers",".\""," Dressing"," in"," layers"," allows"," you"," to"," adjust"," your"," clothing"," to"," suit"," the"," temperature"," and"," your"," level"," of"," exertion","."," Choose"," breathable",","," moisture","-","wick","ing"," fabrics"," that"," won","'","t"," cha","fe"," or"," rub"," against"," your"," skin",".","\n\n","\"","Choose"," the"," right"," shoes",".\"