up","."," Try"," to"," maintain"," a"," consistent"," pace"," throughout"," your"," run",".","\n\n","\"","Pay"," attention"," to"," your"," breathing"," patterns",".\""," Focus"," on"," taking"," deep",","," rhythmic"," breaths"," to"," help"," you"," relax"," and"," find"," a"," consistent"," pace",".","\n\n","\"","Pay"," attention"," to"," your"," posture",".\""," Keep"," your"," head"," up",","," shoulders"," relaxed",","," and"," torso"," upright","."," This"," will"," help"," you"," maintain"," good"," form"," and"," reduce"," your"," risk"," of"," injury",".","\n\n","\"","Practice"," your"," plantar"," flexion"," and"," dor","si","flex","ion",".\""," These"," are"," the"," movements"," that"," occur"," when"," you"," push"," off"," the"," ground"," with"," your"," feet","."," Practice"," flexing"," your"," feet"," and"," ankles"," to"," improve"," your"," running"," form",".","\n\n","\"","Develop"," your"," hip"," joint"," so"," that"," it"," supports"," forward"," motion",".\""," Strong"," hips"," are"," essential"," for"," good"," running"," form","."," Practice"," exercises"," such"," as"," squats"," and"," lung","es"," to"," strengthen"," your"," hip"," joint",".","\n\n","\"","Use"," your"," arms"," to"," propel"," you"," forward",".\""," Keep"," your"," arms"," relaxed"," and"," bent"," at"," around"," a"," ","9","0","-","degree"," angle","."," Use"," your"," arms"," to"," help"," propel"," you"," forward",","," rather"," than"," just"," holding"," them"," still",".","\n\n","\"","Length","en"," your"," stride",".\""," Focus"," on"," taking"," longer",","," more"," efficient"," strides"," to"," improve"," your"," speed"," and"," endurance",".","\n\n","\"","Increase"," your"," stride"," frequency",".\""," Try"," to"," take"," more"," steps"," per"," minute"," to"," increase"," your"," speed","."," This"," will"," take"," practice"," and"," patience",","," but"," it","'","s"," worth"," it"," in"," the"," long"," run",".","\n\n","\"","Begin"," to"," incorpora